title: Team Reticent LF D2+ Top for OOL

embed.description: The latest Tweets from Team Reticent (@TeamReticent). Australian Professional Gaming Organization, featuring teams in DotA 2, CS:GO, SMITE, Rocket League, League of Legends, Call of Duty, Vainglory and Hearthstone!. Australia / International

body: Team Reticent is heading into the OOL with the goal of OCS. If you're a committed player, Diamond 2+ with 5s experience and evening availability for scrims, hit me up.

replies.body:
Eh, I peaked high D2 last season, I'd be more than happy to join. For your curiosity top lane is my secondary, but I've been playing for 5 and a 1/2 years so I understand the dynamics and champs. 

As for 5s experience I've played in 4 full on competitive teams, once in an organisation's sister team and if my  memory serves me correctly 12 semi-competitive friendly teams. I'm usually a mid laner, but I can change on the fly rather easily. 

If you're interested then either reply to my comment or add "Lovesick". Idk how picky you'll be, but my offer is always present.
